                        <h1> Specialty Leasing</h1>

<h3>Eglinton Square Shopping Centre Specialty Leasing</h3>

<p>Eglinton Square is a 286,000 s.f. enclosed shopping centre conveniently located at the intersection of Eglinton
Avenue East and Victoria Park. The Shopping Centre is anchored by the Bay, and Shoppers Drug Mart along with
Metro as a shadow anchor. The mall acts as a community hub with a stable and loyal customer base which
comprises of many seniors and young families. The primary trade area is undergoing a transition from a European
based population to multi ethnic, bringing in new and younger families and a gentrification of the area.
</p> <p>The centre sits in a densely populated area with over and 47,000 households and 126,000 residents within a 3
kilometre radius. Surrounded by mid-century homes, apartments, and new condominium developments, this high
density area continues to grow in demand due to affordability and proximity to Torontoâ€™s downtown core.
</p> <p>Plans for the new Eglinton Light Rail Transit, in approximately 2020, will have stops at the immediate east and
west ends of the Shopping Centre at Victoria Park and Pharmacy Avenue.</p>


